Consider the following pseudocode:

Create empty stack S
Set x = 0, flag = 0, sum = 0
Push x onto S
while (S is not empty) {
    if (flag equals 0) {
        Set x = x + 1
        Push x onto S
    }
    if (x equals 8):
        Set flag = 1
    else {
        Pop from S
        Set sum = sum + x
        Set x = top element of S (without popping)
    }
}

The value of sum output by the above pseudocode is _______ (Answer in integer)
